Achievements.Name: Shut Down
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an enemy mech while its weapons are overheated.

Achievements.Name: EMPowerless
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an enemy while it is under the effect of your EMP.

Achievements.Name: Eye to Eye
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an enemy mech that is zoomed in while you are also zoomed in.

Achievements.Name: Off Guard
Achievements.Description: Eliminated an enemy mech that was currently zoomed in.

Achievements.Name: I've Made a Huge Mistake
Achievements.Description: Deal over 10,000 damage to yourself with your own explosive weapons.

Achievements.Name: Crushed
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an enemy mech by landing on top of it, crushing its robot soul.

Achievements.Name: Survivalist
Achievements.Description: Survive for 15 seconds with less than 10% armor, and then eliminate an enemy mech.

Achievements.Name: Finisher 1
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an enemy mech while it is repairing.

Achievements.Name: Finisher 2
Achievements.Description: Eliminate 10 enemy mechs while they are repairing.

Achievements.Name: Finisher 3
Achievements.Description: Eliminate 100 enemy mechs while they are repairing.

Achievements.Name: Basic Training Certification
Achievements.Description: Complete the final stage of VR Training and receive your Basic Training Certification.
